column5: Just checking to see if this works.
Works fine Gerry...now get back to work..someone's year end is near!
Welcome Gerry.  That yer boat in the avatar? SWEET.  Please,can ya post a larger size.  Thanks  And welcome again
Gerry, you passed, it works and welcome aboard.
Hey Wayne, I've got enough people pushing me ... now you too?  Yes Misfish, that is my boat. Now, let's see if I can post a larger picture.
Nice CLEAN ride Gerry.I see you have the wide screen set up as well.LOL  Cant wait to get mine.  You fish the tourneys?  Thanks for the enlargment.
Couldn't resist Gerry! BTW Gerry is "Firetiger" from the old board guys.

Yes, some CFT and mostly local events. Did the 1 day series last summer but not with my rig; we used mine as a backup. Did the CDN open for 3 years but skipped last summer due to conflict in dates.  You getting a Triton or do you mean a similiar style boat?

Got a boat,it,s in my avatar.350V ranger with a 115.My first.I was talking about your finder/gps on the side mount. Not sure what Im going to get yet.  I did the western bassmania series this season.It was my first year.Had alot of fun.  Up in the air for next year.Want to learn new waters.  I guess you met up with Kulick and Adamo then.Boy those guys had a great year.Good guys.
